  "verses": [
    {
      "num": 1,
      "geez": "ጠየቁ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘውስተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ግብረ፡ እፎ፡ ኢይመይጡ፡ ፍናዊሆሙ፡ ብርሃናት፡ ዘውስተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ከመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ይሠርቅ፡ ወየዐርብ፡ ሥሩዕ፡ ኵሉ፡ በበ፡ ዘመኑ፡ ወኢይትዐደዉ፡ እምትእዛዞሙ።",
      "translation": "Observe ye everything that takes place in the heaven, how they do not change their orbits, and the luminaries which are in the heaven, how they all rise and set in order each in its season, and transgress not against their appointed order.",
